Sentencas: Compared with conventional electric power generation systems, the solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) has many advantages because of its unique features.
Titulo: Status and prospects of intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: High temperature SOFC has been successfully developed to its commercial applications, but it still faces many problems which hamper large-scale commercial applications of SOFC.
Titulo: Status and prospects of intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: To reduce the cost of SOFC, intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC) is presently under rapid development.
Titulo: Status and prospects of intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The status of IT-SOFC was reviewed with emphasis on discussion of their component materials.
Titulo: Status and prospects of intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
